    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. some people I've talked to say that even with the risks, we basically don't have any other realistic option if we want to hit net zero targets in time. like, renewables alone can't handle the baseload. do you think that's a fair assessment or is that just hype?",
      "source": "evaluator"
